{
  "stem": "18626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 46.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the farmers from far away, from miles and miles away, from little towns, from little villages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, the rumors that the Jews are buying bread and green peas and food, and look what I just got.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got earrings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got rings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got silver.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So a lot of farmers start to sneak a little, before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then the ghetto was closed, you couldn't bring anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the-- because the guards would shoot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She brought in, the jewelry, what she had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, she had materials, textile, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my father used to work for textile factories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So sometimes they used to give him a bonus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother bought, you know, she liked to sew a lot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She used to make her own clothes for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was a very good of sewing up things, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was a very talented woman, my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had all the time materials, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] textile materials.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this, when the war broke out, we took call the textile materials into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that helped a lot in the ghetto, when later when I'm going to tell you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we used to take-- because they used to take us out-- out of the ghetto, with guards, to work on the airport, when the Germans were building.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So quietly we used to trade with gentile people, give them a piece of material for a suit, and we used to get a bag 15 or 20 pounds or 10 kilos of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You said, in the house where you were told you were going to live--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already a Jewish Committee, already was-- already established.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
